---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Window from "@components/Window.astro";
import Button from "@components/Button.astro";
import filing from "@assets/icons/filing.png";
import juggler from "@assets/icons/juggler-2.png";
import IconGrid from "@components/IconGrid.astro";
import left from "@assets/icons/left.png";
import right from "@assets/icons/right.png";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Nav from "@components/Nav.astro";
import home from "@assets/icons/home.png";
---

<Layout title="Conclusion" description="This is my conclusion">
  <Window title="Conclusion" close="/desktop">
    <main>
      <h1>Conclusion</h1>
      <p class="description">This is my conclusion</p>
      {
        <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Tag 1</span>
            <span class="tag">Tag 2</span>
            <span class="tag">Tag 3</span>
        </div>
      }
      <main>
        <h1>Hello!</h1>
        <p>
          After 1977, the Apple II demonstrated the relationship between revolution, reaction, and reform. It was a pivotal advancement in technology, sparking demand for accessible, modern personal computers. The revolution caused a positive reaction from the public, leading to the reformation of computer usage in daily life. Without the connection between revolution, reaction, and reform, we would not have more advanced devices today. Devices such as smartphones continue to improve because of reactions. Apple is continuing to come out with revolutionary devices, and this development is driven by demands for reformation. The Apple II is still incredibly relevant today, as the sales of Apple Computers continue to rise consistently. Without the reaction to the Apple II revolution, it would not have caused continuous reformation until today, where we have fully accessible, advanced computers that can be used by everyone. 

        </p>
      </main>
      <IconGrid>
          <Button
            title="Repo"
            icon={filing.src}
            link={`https://github.com/kirinuuu/nhd`}
          />
        
      </IconGrid>
    </main>
    <div class="nav">
      <Nav class="button">
        <a href="/impacts">
          <Image src={left} alt="Previous" />
          <span>Impacts</span>
        </a>
      </Nav>
      <Nav class="button">
        <a href="/"><Image src={home} alt="Home" /></a>
      </Nav>
        <Nav class="button">
          <a href="/documents">
            <span>Documents</span>
            <Image src={right} alt="Next" />
          </a>
        </Nav>
    </div>
  </Window>
</Layout>

<style>
  .nav {
    display: grid;
    width: 100%;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr min-content 1fr;
    align-items: stretch;
    font-family: var(--body-font);
    text-align: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .button {
    display: grid;
  }
  .nav a:link,
  .nav a:visited {
    color: inherit;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    cursor: var(--cursor-pointer);
    font-weight: bold;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .button:last-child a {
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }
  .button:first-child a {
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 800px) {
    .nav span {
      display: none;
    }
    .nav > a {
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .nav > a:last-child {
      display: none;
    }
    .nav > a:first-child {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  .icon-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, 80px);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }
  .description {
    font-size: 18px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: var(--title-font);
    font-weight: normal;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0;
  }
  main {
    font-family: var(--body-font);
    font-size: 18px;
  }
  main :global(a:link),
  main :global(:visited) {
    color: inherit;
    cursor: var(--cursor-pointer);
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }
  .tag {
    background: #fff;
    border: 2px solid #000;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--body-font);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: bold;
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #000;
  }
</style>